snippet.title: Super 8 Football 2023 (Commodore 64)
snippet.description:
Super 8 Football is an American football game using real NFL teams and players. There are 8 playoff teams from last season made up of 16 players with 8 on both offense and defense. The game requires two players, but I hope to have a one-player version available in the future. 

Video capture of gameplay is ok but definitely not the best.

https://interlacedgames.itch.io/super-8-football
